Catalano.Math

Class Vector3

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Math.Vector3

  • public class Vector3
extends java.lang.Object
    3D Vector class with X, Y and Z coordinates. The class incapsulates X, Y and Z coordinates of a 3D vector and provides some operations with it.

      • toVector4

        public Vector4 toVector4()
        Converts the vector to a 4D vector. The method returns a 4D vector which has X, Y and Z coordinates equal to the coordinates of this 3D vector and Vector.W coordinate set to 1.0.
        Returns:
        Returns 4D vector which is an extension of the 3D vector.
